{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-008__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-008", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·008.1", "text_original": "女曰鷄鳴，士曰昧旦。子興視夜，明星有爛。將翱將翔，弋鳧與鴈。", "text_normalized": "女曰鷄鳴，士曰昧旦。子興視夜，明星有爛。將翱將翔，弋鳧與鴈。", "notes": "女曰鷄鳴 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-008__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-008", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·008.2", "text_original": "弋言加之，與子宜之。宜言飲酒，與子偕老。琴瑟在御，莫不靜好。", "text_normalized": "弋言加之，與子宜之。宜言飲酒，與子偕老。琴瑟在御，莫不靜好。", "notes": "女曰鷄鳴 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhengfeng-008__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-008", "source_id": "guofeng-zhengfeng-008__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄭風·008.3", "text_original": "知子之來之，雜佩以贈之。知子之順之，雜佩以問之。知子之好之，雜佩以報之。", "text_normalized": "知子之來之，雜佩以贈之。知子之順之，雜佩以問之。知子之好之，雜佩以報之。", "notes": "女曰鷄鳴 Chinese stanza 3."}
